# IntelliJ HTTP Client examples for technical-interview-demo
# Category creation requires ADMIN, an authenticated session, and CSRF.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@sessionCookie = paste-technical-interview-demo-session-here
@csrfToken = paste-x-csrf-token-here

### CategoryController - list categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Accept: application/json

### CategoryController - create category (ADMIN + authenticated + CSRF)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
X-CSRF-TOKEN: {{csrfToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Architecture"
}
